WEBVTT

00:00:01.480 --> 00:00:02.550
Duela urtebete inguru,

00:00:03.490 --> 00:00:05.040
zera galdetu nion neure buruari:

00:00:05.630 --> 00:00:06.760
"Dakidana jakinda,

00:00:07.690 --> 00:00:09.280
zergatik ez naiz begetarianoa?"

00:00:10.220 --> 00:00:11.000
Azken finean,

00:00:11.770 --> 00:00:12.820
ingurumenak axola dit:

00:00:12.950 --> 00:00:15.520
Guraso hippy bik hazi ninduten
egurrezko etxola batean.

00:00:16.210 --> 00:00:18.580
"TreeHugger" izeneko web-orria
sortu nuen.

00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:22.390
Kontu horiek axola didate.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:26.530
Banekien egunean
hanburgesa bakarra jate hutsak

00:00:26.550 --> 00:00:28.760
hiltzeko arriskua heren batean
handitzen zuela.

